'''黎逸'''（{{Lang-th|ร้อยเอ็ด}}，{{IPA-th|rɔ́ːj ʔèt|pron}}）是一個位於[[泰國|泰國]][[依善地区|依善地区]]的城鎮，亦為[[黎逸府|黎逸府]]的首府。<ref>{{cite web|title=Roi Et|url=http://www.tourismthailand.org/Where-to-Go/Roi-Et|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623141544/http://www.tourismthailand.org/Where-to-Go/Roi-Et|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-06-23|website=Tourism Authority of Thailand (TAT)|accessdate=2015-06-21|language=en}}</ref>在2019年，全鎮人口約36,225人。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.citypopulation.de/en/thailand/northeastern/45__roi_et/ |title=ROI ET |website=citypopulation.de |language=en |access-date=2020-11-01 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101131522/https://www.citypopulation.de/en/thailand/northeastern/45__roi_et/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>距離[[曼谷|曼谷]]約514公里。<ref>{{cite web|title=Distance Bangkok-Roi Et|url=http://www.distancesfrom.com/th/distance-from-Bangkok-to-Roi-Et-Thailand/DistanceHistory/2155056.aspx|website=DistancesFrom.com|accessdate=2015-06-21|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621124035/http://www.distancesfrom.com/th/distance-from-Bangkok-to-Roi-Et-Thailand/DistanceHistory/2155056.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==氣候==
黎逸擁有[[熱帶乾濕季氣候|熱帶乾濕季氣候]]（[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]Aw），冬天乾燥溫暖，氣溫上升至4月時非常炎熱，平均每日最高溫度為{{convert|35.7|°C|°F}}。[[季風|季風]]季節從5月到10月，白天有大雨和稍涼的氣溫，但夜晚仍然維持溫暖。

