== 交通 ==
黎逸有多條公路來往周邊府份和城市，包括{{link-en|馬哈沙拉堪|Maha Sarakham}}、{{link-en|班派縣|Ban Phai District}}、{{link-en|益梭通|Yasothon}}、[[乌汶叻差他尼|烏汶]]等地。黎逸亦擁有一個位於城鎮北部的{{link-en|黎逸機場|Roi Et Airport}}，提供來往曼谷的班機服務。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rob Muang Airport|url=http://www.ourairports.com/airports/VTUR/|publisher=OurAirports|accessdate=2013-02-04|language=en|archive-date=2013-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729175809/http://www.ourairports.com/airports/VTUR/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.airasia.com/flights/from-roi-et-roi-to-bangkok-dmk |title=Roi Et to Bangkok Flights |publisher=AirAsia |access-date=2020-11-01 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101131512/https://www.airasia.com/flights/from-roi-et-roi-to-bangkok-dmk |dead-url=no }}</ref>

